org.gbif.registry

Class DatasetOccurrenceDownloadIT

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.registry.DatasetOccurrenceDownloadIT

  • public class DatasetOccurrenceDownloadIT
extends Object
    Runs tests for the OccurrenceDownloadService implementations. This is parameterized to run the same test routines for the following:
    1. The persistence layer
    2. The WS service layer
    3. The WS service client layer
